text: Tim Storm (born 19 July 1956) is a Canadian rower. He competed in the men's double sculls event at the 1984 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1956 births Category:Living people Category:Canadian male rowers Category:Olympic rowers of Canada Category:Rowers at the 1984 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Rotterdam Category:Pan American Games medalists in rowing Category:Pan American Games gold medalists for Canada Category:Rowers at the 1979 Pan American Games
